            In short, you could view the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Florida Atlantic</ENAMEX> program as a version of
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Harvard</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Kennedy School of Government</ENAMEX>, except it's for left-wing <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">activists</ENAMEX>
