<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">platoon</ENAMEX> of quasi-subsidized publishing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">companies</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Free Press</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Basic Books</ENAMEX>,
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Public Affairs Press</ENAMEX>, etc.) ready to print them. On the other hand, why should
